51.6	Casino_(film)	Casino (film)	Casino is a 1995 crime drama film directed by Martin Scorsese. It is based on the non-fiction book of the same name by Nicholas Pileggi, who also co-wrote the screenplay for the film with Scorsese. The two previously collaborated on the 1990 hit film Goodfellas.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d8/Casino_poster.jpg/220px-Casino_poster.jpg
